From the Infowars web site ::

On the Friday, November 18 edition of the Alex Jones Show, Alex hosts the show from the road. He talks with trends forecaster and the publisher of the Trends Journal, Gerald Celente, about the MF Global scandal and the meltdown of the futures market. Celente is the author of the national best-seller, Trends 2000: How to Prepare for and Profit from the Changes of the 21st Century. 

editor and co-host of Infowars Nightly News, Aaron Dykes, also talks with Alex.
